    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Hm so unfortunately, `axios-retry` won't work for interfacing with Etherscan.  (We can use it for Sourcify!  But not Etherscan.)  The problem is that `axios-retry` doesn't allow retrying on a 200 OK response, but Etherscan often indicates errors by sending a 200 OK and then indicating the error in the body.  So, that won't work here.  (I've filed [an issue](https://github.com/softonic/axios-retry/issues/171) with them, FWIW.)",
